data.description: Welcome Home to Glenwood Hills! Traditional ranch floor plan complete with formal living and dining room, separate den with fireplace and bright open kitchen with a kitchen sink picture window looking up at the Sandias. New roof and fresh with all new flooring in the living areas, and bright neutral paint throughout all you have to do is pick out your bedroom and come meet your new neighbors! Convenient foothills location close to shopping, open space and trails, parks, city lights and mountain views all around.  Neighborhood deer and bunnies come to visit regularly so be sure to drive slowly and enjoy the sites. Glenwood Hills is a great foothills area to explore and reside with quick access to I-25 and I-40 for ease of travel all around the metro area. Welcome to Glenwood Hills!
